---
title: Sausage & Veggie Tray Bake with Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: Sausages, bangers, snags - whatever you like to call them, these pork delights are heaven on a tray! We've teamed them with loads of baked veggies for goodness and a creamy pesto dressing that lifts this dish to next-level tastiness. Gather the troops and get ready for a dinner that really sizzles!
